title: Isileli Tupou
text: Isileli Tupou also known as Kaiongo Tupou (born 26 October 1984) in <a href="Tofua">Tofua</a>, <a href="Tonga">Tonga</a>) is a <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays at center. He currently plays with the Lille Métropole Rugby in the Federale 1 in France.
